# 📝 Project Abstraction – Course Management System (MERN Stack)

## 📌 Objective

To develop a simple, full-stack Course Management System where users can:
- Add course details (title & description)
- View all added courses
- Interact via a clean React frontend

## 📦 Stack Used

- MongoDB (in-memory memory-server for lightweight DB)
- Express.js for backend API
- React.js for frontend UI
- Node.js as server environment
- Axios for HTTP requests

## 🧠 Why this project?

- Demonstrates end-to-end MERN integration
- No external database dependency (MongoDB memory server)
- Ideal for learning CRUD operations and full stack structure

## ⚙️ Core Features

- POST /courses → Add new course
- GET /courses → Fetch all courses
- React-based interactive UI
- State-driven rendering & live updates
